1
00:00:01,200 --> 00:00:03,600
That big case I mentioned.

2
00:00:03,600 --> 00:00:06,270
If something goes wrong
with the partnership agreement...

3
00:00:06,970 --> 00:00:08,210
The losses could reach a billion yen.

4
00:00:08,210 --> 00:00:09,610
That's no small sum.

5
00:00:09,610 --> 00:00:10,680
For a billion yen...

6
00:00:11,510 --> 00:00:13,710
How about you buy one day of my time?

7
00:00:14,850 --> 00:00:15,980
I see.

8
00:00:17,320 --> 00:00:18,690
Maybe next time, then.

9
00:00:27,260 --> 00:00:29,500
Women...

10
00:00:29,530 --> 00:00:31,130
They're no match for men.

11
00:00:33,400 --> 00:00:34,900
All they're good for is having babies.

12
00:00:36,070 --> 00:00:37,570
Just a body with an extra hole.

13
00:00:47,550 --> 00:00:48,780
Disgusting.

14
00:00:49,250 --> 00:00:50,280
A man like that...

15
00:00:50,780 --> 00:00:52,050
I have absolutely no interest in him.

16
00:00:52,850 --> 00:00:53,850
But...

17
00:00:53,990 --> 00:00:55,960
To get my revenge on that woman,

18
00:00:56,520 --> 00:00:58,160
I've decided I'll do whatever it takes.

19
00:01:01,900 --> 00:01:04,730
This is our new legal counsel,
Makishima Reika.

20
00:01:06,400 --> 00:01:07,400
Ever since that day,

21
00:01:07,900 --> 00:01:09,570
not a day has gone by

22
00:01:09,570 --> 00:01:10,840
that I've forgotten her.

23
00:01:12,010 --> 00:01:14,110
And I hate myself for being unable to forget her.

24
00:01:14,710 --> 00:01:16,710
This is my lovely wife.

25
00:01:16,710 --> 00:01:17,710
Oh, honestly.

26
00:01:18,510 --> 00:01:20,210
My wife is a culinary expert.

27
00:01:20,210 --> 00:01:22,080
She runs a cooking school,

28
00:01:22,180 --> 00:01:24,220
and for our company,

29
00:01:24,220 --> 00:01:25,620
she also manages
the cooking app.

30
00:01:25,750 --> 00:01:27,590
Looking so happy with another man,
right in front of me.

31
00:01:27,590 --> 00:01:28,790
This woman before me

32
00:01:29,760 --> 00:01:31,720
stirred up a dark emotion

33
00:01:32,490 --> 00:01:34,230
that I just couldn't suppress.

34
00:01:36,330 --> 00:01:37,530
You two need to
get along now.

35
00:01:38,470 --> 00:01:39,470
Okay?

36
00:01:43,400 --> 00:01:46,040
I'm going to take everything
from that woman.

37
00:01:46,040 --> 00:01:47,310
By any means necessary.
